iPad-self-contained live app: proxy APIs, live signals, Compare, News

Major restructure to make the app a true self-contained iPad learning pad.
All data now fetched live from public APIs through four Vercel serverless
proxies; no CSVs, no Python, no API keys needed.

New serverless functions (standalone/api/):
- fx.js     - Frankfurter (ECB) AUD/USD daily history + latest
- gold.js   - Yahoo Finance GC=F gold daily history + latest
- news.js   - GDELT Doc API headlines (AUD/RBA/Fed/gold/risk, 72h English)
- rates.js  - Hand-maintained RBA + Fed policy rates

vercel.json configured for Node 20 functions + CORS + caching.

standalone/trade.html fully rewritten as a seven-tab live app:
- Now     - live AUD/USD + gold + rates, Chameleon/Catchup computed in
            browser from fetched history, consensus card, Explain-this
            drop-downs on every card, status pills
- Compare - AUD vs gold normalised chart (30d/90d/180d/1y), correlation,
            beta, regime context vs 1-year baseline
- News    - GDELT feed filterable by topic (all/AUD/RBA/Fed/gold/risk-off)
- Sandbox - replays the live-fetched history instead of baked JSON; keeps
            save/export/import to iPad Files / Drive
- Journal - unchanged; export/import stays
- Learn   - expanded with collapsible glossary, strategy explainers,
            'what can go wrong'
- Health  - runs live proxy checks, 0/6 readiness score

Deleted baked daily JSON files (chameleon_data, catchup_data, *_history).
App no longer needs offline updaters; the Python scripts still exist in
scripts/ for anyone doing offline research.

docs/USER_GUIDE.md rewritten to document the new architecture, including
honest notes that prices are daily not intraday, and how to update the
hand-maintained rates when the RBA/Fed change policy.

Tested upstream APIs end-to-end:
- Frankfurter: OK, 200 per call
- Yahoo gold: OK, 254-bar 1y history parseable
- GDELT: OK, 200 + real articles once upstream 5s-per-IP rate limit clears;
  proxy returns friendly 429 with retry_after when throttled
- rates: pure function, shape verified
